1. Table 'client_offering_mapping' field 'isConverted' defines whether a client has been converted to 
   existing client or not for a particular product.
   0 Not converted
   1 Converted
   2 Lost Client
2. Table 'client_takeaction' field 'isFinished' defines whether an action has been completed or not
   0 Incomplete
   1 Finished
   
      



